Package: MLTS
Title: Machine Learning for Time Series
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Eric", "Brist", email = "eric.brist@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains functions for time series forecasting using machine learning methods. 
    The methods include random forest, extreme gradient boosting, and support vector machine. 
    Functions for ARIMA and dynamic harmonic regression forecasting are also provided. 
    Simulation functions are also included to compare the performance of these methods on specific forms of time series data.
Depends:
  R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
  data.table,
  dplyr,
  ggplot2,
  gridExtra,
  pander,
  tibble,
  randomForest,
  smooth,
  plotly,
  e1071,
  xgboost,
  forecast
